pma:database.name: camprecon
pma:database.pma:table: CREATE TABLE `tblcourse` ( `strCourseID` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strCourseName` varchar(45) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strDeptCode` varchar(4) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strGenEdCategory` varchar(3) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `strPrerequisite` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `strCorequisite` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `intCredits` int(1) NOT NULL, `dblFee` float NOT NULL, `strCourseDescription` varchar(140) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`strCourseID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `tbldepartment` ( `intDeptID` tinyint(3) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `strDeptCode` varchar(4) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strDeptName` varchar(32) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`intDeptID`), UNIQUE KEY `strDeptCode` (`strDeptCode`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=109 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `tblfacility` ( `intFacilityID` int(7) NOT NULL, `strFacilityName` varchar(64) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strStreet` varchar(32) NOT NULL, `strCity` varchar(16) NOT NULL, `strState` varchar(2) NOT NULL, `strPostCode` varchar(9) NOT NULL, `intLongitude` float NOT NULL, `intLatitude` float NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`intFacilityID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `tblfaculty` ( `intFacultyID` int(7) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `strLastName` varchar(24) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strFirstName` varchar(24) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strMiddleName` varchar(24) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `intDeptID` tinyint(3) unsigned NOT NULL, `strPosition` varchar(40) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `blnAdvisor` varchar(1) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strFacultyEID` varchar(24) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `intSecurityGroup` int(3) unsigned NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `strPhone` varchar(11) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`intFacultyID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=17 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `tblroom` ( `intRoomID` int(5) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `intFacilityID` int(7) NOT NULL, `strRoomNumber` varchar(5) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `intSeats` int(3) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`intRoomID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=17 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `tblsection` ( `intSectionID` int(12) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `intSectionNumber` tinyint(3) unsigned NOT NULL, `strCourseID` varchar(10) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `intRoomID` int(5) NOT NULL, `intFacultyID` int(7) unsigned NOT NULL, `intTimeSlotID` int(3) NOT NULL, `intScheduleID` int(3) unsigned NOT NULL, `intYear` int(4) NOT NULL, `strSeason` varchar(8) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `dtmStartDate` date NOT NULL, `dtmEndDate` date NOT NULL, `intCapacity` int(3) NOT NULL, `intWaitlistTotal` int(3) NOT NULL, `blnOnlineSection` tinyint(1) NOT NULL, `strRequiredText` varchar(25) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`intSectionID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=32 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `tblstudent` ( `intStudentID` int(7) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `intFacultyID` int(7) unsigned NOT NULL, `strFirstName` varchar(24) NOT NULL, `strLastName` varchar(24) NOT NULL, `strMiddleName` varchar(24) DEFAULT NULL, `strStudentEID` varchar(40) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strStatus` varchar(8) NOT NULL, `strEnrollmentStatus` varchar(8) NOT NULL, `strStudentType` varchar(3) NOT NULL, `strMajor1` varchar(20) NOT NULL, `strMajor2` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `strMajor3` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `strMinor1` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `strMinor2` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `strMinor3` varchar(20) DEFAULT NULL, `dblGPA` float DEFAULT NULL, `dblDues` float DEFAULT NULL, `intCredits` int(3) DEFAULT NULL, `blnActiveService` tinyint(1) DEFAULT NULL, `intSecurityGroup` int(3) NOT NULL, `dtmDateOfBirth` date DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`intStudentID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `tblstudentenrollment` ( `intStudentID` int(7) NOT NULL, `intSectionID` int(12) NOT NULL, `strSectionGrade` varchar(2) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `strEnrollmentStatus` varchar(1) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `strPermitStatus` varchar(1) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `intWaitlistPosition` int(3) DEFAULT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`intStudentID`,`intSectionID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `tbltask` ( `intTaskID` int(12) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `strEID` varchar(40) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `intTaskTypeID` int(11) unsigned NOT NULL, `strReason` varchar(64) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `dblAmount` decimal(10,2) DEFAULT NULL, `strStatus` varchar(16) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `dtmIssued` date DEFAULT NULL, `dtmDue` date DEFAULT NULL, `strDepartment` varchar(128) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`intTaskID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `tbltasktype` ( `intTaskTypeID` int(10) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `strTypeName` varchar(64) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strTaskClass` char(1) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strInstruction` varchar(512) COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`intTaskTypeID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=6 DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci;

CREATE TABLE `tbluser` ( `intUserId` int(8) unsigned NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `strEID` varchar(45) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strPassword` varchar(64) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, PRIMARY KEY (`intUserId`), UNIQUE KEY `strEID` (`strEID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=3 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;

CREATE TABLE `tblusercontact` ( `intContactID` int(7) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `strExternalEID` varchar(45) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strCountry` varchar(30) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strStreet` varchar(30) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strCity` varchar(30) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strState` varchar(30) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strPostCode` varchar(9) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci NOT NULL, `strMobileNumber` varchar(11) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `strHomeNumber` varchar(11) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `strEmail` varchar(64) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `strEmergencyNumber` varchar(11) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `strEmergencyContactType` varchar(15) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `strEmergencyContactLastName` varchar(24) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `strEmergencyContactFirstName` varchar(24) CHARACTER SET utf8 COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci DEFAULT NULL, `blnEmergencyContact` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `blnMailingAddress` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `blnPermanent` tinyint(1) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', PRIMARY KEY (`intContactID`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB AUTO_INCREMENT=9 DEFAULT CHARSET=latin1;
